wait to hear about the big collections coming to market in November. <br/><=
br/>Tonight, I=E2=80=99ve got a little news about UTA=E2=80=99s Fine Arts d=
ivision that also offers a good opportunity to discuss the changing structu=
re of the art market. UTA may be out of the art business, but the demand am=
ong artists for a business surrogate=E2=80=94someone who can act like an ag=
